","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"e5d1e5c58ab23ce38cd1e143caf71bca99db98ee","tid":1729172,"uid":338712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:50:26.000Z","msg":"以上次中大一戰作參考，晚上有好大機會發生激烈衝突，加上popo經上次一役之後，戰術必有改善，<br />\n<br />\n而且中大一戰，popo只派一水炮車，<br />\n對比今次(一水炮、二鋭武、音波炮），而且旺角與poly非常近，所以加上旺角警力，可説popo今次差唔多總動員到poly<br />\n<br />\n另外學校報警、示威者取危險物品、使用弓箭、巨型亞叉等，popo可以此藉口，全面進入校園拘捕或使用致命武力。這必令各手足有慘重傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為popo正等待夜晚，街上人流減少，然後開戰。<br />\n<br />\n各前線手足，如果popo有任何唔妥，請唔好留，唔好送頭，唔好受傷，我哋一個都不能少。<br />\n<br />\n其他人，可選擇各區花、到中環集會或到poly支援。"},{"pid":"be27c5f55529c0901f2632c69760e041d18ab417","tid":1729172,"uid":116486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:53:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1ec9e18fb823f13071907cb71fc5d32fe605524a","tid":1729172,"uid":12920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7acdf424e49d6c946a9a36a5842570291616ba7","tid":1729172,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9feb09741f360d9b3e085b6c12c4d704e0e5eecc","tid":1729172,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:59:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"318f46cbe06603531a78ab22534d763fbc0924f2","tid":1729172,"uid":207543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:00:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcd324a2b15bbd45975719e55a028e290a7b8b33","tid":1729172,"uid":207543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e71ec63a33bb99b48412e4187cbcfaad16734f1","tid":1729172,"uid":207543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,